mall;"><em>Rezvanian H</em></span></a><em><span style="font-size: small;">, </span></em><a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/sites/entrez?Db=pubmed&amp;Cmd=Search&amp;Term=%22Amini%20M%22%5BAuthor%5D&amp;itool=EntrezSystem2.PEntrez.Pubmed.Pubmed_ResultsPanel.Pubmed_RVAbstract"><span style="color: #0000ff; font-size: small;"><em>Amini M</em></span></a><em><span style="font-size: small;">, </span></em><a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/sites/entrez?Db=pubmed&amp;Cmd=Search&amp;Term=%22Mirmiran%20P%22%5BAuthor%5D&amp;itool=EntrezSystem2.PEntrez.Pubmed.Pubmed_ResultsPanel.Pubmed_RVAbstract"><span style="color: #0000ff; font-size: small;"><em>Mirmiran P</em></span></a><em><span style="font-size: small;">. </span></em><em><span style="font-size: small;">Urinary iodine excretion in pregnant women residing in areas with adequate iodine intake.<span style="color: #0000ff;">Public Health Nutr.</span> 2003 Feb;6(1):95-8.</span></em></p>\r\n<p><em><span style="font-size: small;">8.</span></em>     <a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/sites/entrez?Db=pubmed&amp;Cmd=Search&amp;Term=%22Marchioni%20E%22%5BAuthor%5D&amp;itool=EntrezSystem2.PEntrez.Pubmed.Pubmed_ResultsPanel.Pubmed_RVAbstract"><span style="color: #0000ff; font-size: small;"><em>Marchioni E</em></span></a><em><span style="font-size: small;">, <a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/sites/entrez?Db=pubmed&amp;Cmd=Search&amp;Term=%22Fumarola%20A%22%5BAuthor%5D&amp;itool=EntrezSystem2.PEntrez.Pubmed.Pubmed_ResultsPanel.Pubmed_RVAbstract"><span style="color: #0000ff;">Fumarola A</span></a>, <a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/sites/entrez?Db=pubmed&amp;Cmd=Search&amp;Term=%22Calvanese%20A%22%5BAuthor%5D&amp;itool=EntrezSystem2.PEntrez.Pubmed.Pubmed_ResultsPanel.Pubmed_RVAbstract"><span style="color: #0000ff;">Calvanese A</span></a>, <a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/sites/entrez?Db=pubmed&amp;Cmd=Search&amp;Term=%22Piccirilli%20F%22%5BAuthor%5D&amp;itool=EntrezSystem2.PEntrez.Pubmed.Pubmed_ResultsPanel.Pubmed_RVAbstrac